{"id":125106,"type":1,"name":"蒼のマハラジャ","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/95/ab/125106_3ksdo.jpg","summary":"西元1939-1945年，世界第二次世界大戰爆發，\r\n隨後而來的是亞非地區蓬勃發展的獨立運動浪潮，\r\n一邊是殖民母國對既得利益的不甘放手，\r\n一邊被殖民國對獨立自主的渴求希冀，\r\n在兩股力量的碰撞激盪中，\r\n英國大使之女茉依隨著父親抵達了富裕的印度藩國‧喬多布爾。\r\n沒料到的是，在這一趟印度之行，\r\n茉依與喬多布爾王子‧西爾的邂逅，徹底的改變了雙方的人生。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>印度恋曲</li><li><span>册数: </span>10</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/40770\">神坂智子</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/518\">角川書店</a>、<a href=\"/person/7033\">東立出版社</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8516\">月刊Asuka</a></li><li><span>开始: </span>1990年3月号</li><li><span>结束: </span>1993年6月号</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"漫画系列","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":40770,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ac/b2/40770_prsn_Qzg2g.jpg","name":"神坂智子","desc":"作者"},{"id":7033,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fd/24/7033_prsn_J3N83.jpg","name":"东立出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":518,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5a/52/518_prsn_ZwMWM.jpg","name":"角川书店","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8516,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/15/13/8516_prsn_pKJG1.jpg","name":"月刊Asuka","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":125177,"name":"蒼のマハラジャ 1","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/ca/c1/125177_jp.jpg"},{"id":125108,"name":"蒼のマハラジャ 2","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/73/4e/125108_jp.jpg"},{"id":125110,"name":"蒼のマハラジャ 3","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/60/a3/125110_jp.jpg"},{"id":125109,"name":"蒼のマハラジャ 4","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/5e/84/125109_jp.jpg"},{"id":125111,"name":"蒼のマハラジャ 5","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/46/3e/125111_jp.jpg"},{"id":125112,"name":"蒼のマハラジャ 6","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/"},{"id":125113,"name":"蒼のマハラジャ 7","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/"},{"id":125115,"name":"蒼のマハラジャ 8","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/"},{"id":125116,"name":"蒼のマハラジャ 9","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/"},{"id":125117,"name":"蒼のマハラジャ 10","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/"}]}